e and vegetables","content":["300 g white rice","900 g water","1 bunch tenderstem broccoli (approx. 180 g), trimmed and cut in thirds","230 g tinned bamboo shoots, rinsed and drained (weight is pre-draining)","1 spring onion, trimmed and thinly sliced, for garnishing","1 - 2 sprigs fresh coriander, leaves only, for garnishing"]}],"id":"r146838","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-6p5RqomfQOI\/XZQHlVEKqDI\/AAAAAAAAcJ0\/quMf6x6AVq4DBK1DLBccVcoEuBNdpadNwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_mx3KczdnIzz9MpL4.png","title":"Pork with Black Bean Sauce","publishedAt":"2017-09-04T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"33.8 g","fat":"3.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"55.2 g","calories":"1726 kJ \/ 411 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large serving bowl","basicInfo":["easy","20m","30m","6 portions"]}